raw: Gives your team's next ball/bomb, pulse, recharge, breath and two-turn move x1.5 dmg. Stacks 8x.

POLARVORTEX.name: Polar Vortex
POLARVORTEX.desc: This howling gale switches out the target for a random ally. The user flinches if hit first.
raw: This howling gale switches out the target for a random ally. The user flinches if hit first.

TRANSCISION.name: Transcision
TRANSCISION.desc: Scalpels and mixes fluids with the target. Each first use, swaps items with the target.
raw: Scalpels and mixes fluids with the target. Each first use, swaps items with the target.

TREACHEREEDS.name: Treachereeds
TREACHEREEDS.desc: If itemless, this cunning bushcraft attack makes the user a substitute using 1/4 Max HP.
raw: If itemless, this cunning bushcraft attack makes the user a substitute using 1/4 Max HP.

PESTER.name: Pester
PESTER.desc: Disables enemies' Paragon Moves, Torments them, and cuts 1 PP from their moves for 8 turns.
raw: Disables enemies' Paragon Moves, Torments them, and cuts 1 PP from their moves for 8 turns.

BEASTWITHIN.name: Beast Within
BEASTWITHIN.desc: Uses the target's lower base defending stat. Can't be used in conjunction with allies' Special attacks.
raw: Uses the target's lower base defending stat. Can't be used in conjunction with allies' Special attacks.

GROUNDZERO.name: Ground Zero
GROUNDZERO.desc: Uses the target's lower base defending stat. Can't be used in conjunction with allies' Physical attacks.
raw: Uses the target's lower base defending stat. Can't be used in conjunction with allies' Physical attacks.

UNCANNYVALLEY.name: Uncanny Valley
UNCANNYVALLEY.desc: Something feels off... Transforms the target into a copy of the user, except for HP.
raw: Something feels off... Transforms the target into a copy of the user, except for HP.

SLIPPERYSLOPE.name: Slippery Slope
SLIPPERYSLOPE.desc: Boosting moves raise allies' Speed. Can't be used in conjunction with moves over 80 power.
raw: Boosting moves raise allies' Speed. Can't be used in conjunction with moves over 80 power.

WEEPINGABSCESS.name: Weeping Abscess
WEEPINGABSCESS.desc: This uncontrolled, malignant attack has a 20% chance to raise the user's Sp. Attack.
raw: This uncontrolled, malignant attack has a 20% chance to raise the user's Sp. Attack.

CEASELESSMALICE.name: Ceaseless Malice
CEASELESSMALICE.desc: Commences a horror movie-esque assault for 3 turns, then becomes Paralyzed.
raw: Commences a horror movie-esque assault for 3 turns, then becomes Paralyzed.

ELECTRICCHAIR.name: Electric Chair
ELECTRICCHAIR.desc: This deadly current uses the higher attacking stat, but cuts 3 PP from allies' moves for 2 turns.
raw: This deadly current uses the higher attacking stat, but cuts 3 PP from allies' moves for 2 turns.

SPREADINGPLAGUE.name: Spreading Plague
SPREADINGPLAGUE.desc: Spreads a deadly airborne plague onto enemies. 30% chance to leave Compound Gas.
raw: Spreads a deadly airborne plague onto enemies. 30% chance to leave Compound Gas.

PYRRHICVICTORY.name: Pyrrhic Victory
PYRRHICVICTORY.desc: For 5 procs each, residual damage and healing effects, except weather, have 1/16th more effectiveness.
raw: For 5 procs each, residual damage and healing effects, except weather, have 1/16th more effectiveness.

POISONEDPAWN.name: Poisoned Pawn
POISONEDPAWN.desc: Makes a substitute using 1/4 Max HP which prevents the user from being damaged or statused until broken.
raw: Makes a substitute using 1/4 Max HP which prevents the user from being damaged or statused until broken.

WINDBREAKER.name: Guardian Windbreaker
WINDBREAKER.desc: Sets the target's Critical Hit Ratio to -4, then heals 1/8 Max HP per Crit stage lowered by this effect.
raw: Sets the target's Critical Hit Ratio to -4, then heals 1/8 Max HP per Crit stage lowered by this effect.

SKYSPLITTER.name: Guardian Skysplitter
SKYSPLITTER.desc: Leaves a Lightning Chain and has +20 power for each of the target's stat changes.
raw: Leaves a Lightning Chain and has +20 power for each of the target's stat changes.

MUTATION.name: Guardian Mutation
MUTATION.desc: Deals 1/4th Max HP dmg to active opponents each turn, for 3 procs. Also creates 3 Compound Gas procs.
raw: Deals 1/4th Max HP dmg to active opponents each turn, for 3 procs. Also creates 3 Compound Gas procs.

INVASION.name: Guardian Invasion
INVASION.desc: Restores HP equal to 75% damage dealt. Deals x2 damage to Compromised targets. Requires a recharge turn.
raw: Restores HP equal to 75% damage dealt. Deals x2 damage to Compromised targets. Requires a recharge turn.

BOTTLEDLIGHTNING.name: Bottled Lightning
BOTTLEDLIGHTNING.desc: The user catches lightning, doubling the Sp. Atk of active allies for 4 turns.
raw: The user catches lightning, doubling the Sp. Atk of active allies for 4 turns.

COMPACTOR.name: Compactor
COMPACTOR.desc: A churning, crushing attack that also eliminates entry hazards and effects like Bind or Leech Seed.
raw: A churning, crushing attack that also eliminates entry hazards and effects like Bind or Leech Seed.

EUREKA.name: Eureka!
EUREKA.desc: This brilliant attack consumes the user's item to erect 5 turns of Industrial Grade.
raw: This brilliant attack consumes the user's item to erect 5 turns of Industrial Grade.

CHARITY.name: Guardian Charity
CHARITY.desc: Cures any status or Compromising effects, casts Lucky Chant, and Cotton Spore.
raw: Cures any status or Compromising effects, casts Lucky Chant, and Cotton Spore.

HORTICULTURE.name: Guardian Horticulture
HORTICULTURE.desc: Traps the target. Triggers a Phazard, such as Vine Snare, on the opponent's field. High Crit ratio. Never misses.
raw: Traps the target. Triggers a Phazard, such as Vine Snare, on the opponent's field. High Crit ratio. Never misses.

SPLICE.name: Guardian Splice
SPLICE.desc: Replaces this move with the target's move, reduces the target's move's PP to 0, then heals based on the PP lost.
raw: Replaces this move with the target's move, reduces the target's move's PP to 0, then heals based on the PP lost.

STRAND.name: Guardian Strand
STRAND.desc: Casts a Rocky Payload, then cuts 4 PP from opponents' moves and slightly lowers their Accuracy each turn for 8 turns.
raw: Casts a Rocky Payload, then cuts 4 PP from opponents' moves and slightly lowers their Accuracy each turn for 8 turns.

ASCENSION.name: Guardian Ascension
ASCENSION.desc: Increases Attack, Def, Sp. Atk, Sp. Def, and Speed 1 stage for each opposing fainted Pokemon.
raw: Increases Attack, Def, Sp. Atk, Sp. Def, and Speed 1 stage for each opposing fainted Pokemon.
